            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Pumpkin House is one of the best thing happened to us when we were looking for a play school post covid.\n\nOne of the main thing we were looking was safe environment and personal attention to our child since these kids were home bound due to  covid19.\n\nPumpkin house has undoubtedly did an excellent job of providing the best to our child's development from comforting atmosphere, fun activities and loving faculty.\n\nYou get regular updates, teachers are hands-on and every body there is full of warmth and love.\n\nWe truly enjoyed our journey with Pumpkin House. Kudos to the entire team.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
