            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "I think I made the best choice to enroll my child in Pumpkin house play school. It’s great to hear so many classroom tales from my girl each day.\nI appreciate the efforts made by the whole staff, teachers, principal ma'am,  didis to make the stay so comfortable and joyful for kids..\nEveryone is very professional, caring and well organized..\nHighly recommended!!",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "itemReviewed": {
