          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "My daughter has been going to pumpkin house since the past 6 months now and I am happy with the experience and her learning.\nWe did thorough research before choosing her school and if fancy/modern infra is not your primary reason of choosing a school, pumpkin house is the right choice for your kid.\nSpecial mention to Alka mam who is a delight to interact with and creates positive vibes right from the reception to the classroom.\nLast but not the least, one of my reasons of choosing pumpkin house was Sarah Ma’am and I can confidently say that your child is in the best hands if he/she is in her class.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "itemReviewed": {
            "@type": "School",
            "name": "Pumpkin House Playschool - Sector 43"
          },
          "author": {
            "@type": "Person",
            "name": "Anupam Jain"
          },
          "datePublished": "2023-01-23",
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Such an amazing playschool. This was always quite near to our place but we never knew how amazing the school and management is until our younger one started going there. Anita mam, especially, is super caring. She takes care of them as her own. She would do whatever to make sure the child gets the best (even if it means scolding us :D). Deepa mam, who heads the school is very nice - her personal connect with each child is worth appreciation. We are glad we made this choice.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
